item.title: CVE-2020-2123|2024-08-04T07:01:40.685Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20radargun%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins RadarGun Plugin 1.7 and earlier does not configure its YAML parser to prevent the instantiation of arbitrary types, resulting in a remote code execution vulnerability.
